data.name: textOptionsCombo.HelpString
data.value:
Specifies Whether text descriptions of the toolbar buttons appear in the toolbar and where the text appears.
To display the names of the buttons underneath each button on the toolbar, click "Show text labels".
To display the names of certain buttons such as "Search" and "Back", click "Selective text on right". The text will appear on the right or left side of the button depending on current locale settings.
To show only icons on the toolbar, click "No text labels".

data.name: iconOptionsCombo.HelpString
data.value: Changes the size of the icons in the Toolbar. These changes will appear after you have closed the "Customize ToolBar" dialog.
